# ğŸŒ± Lysimeter Weight Logging System

This system uses Arduino to measure and log the weight from two different load cell configurations â€” one using four load cells, and another using a single load cell. Data is saved to an SD card with a real-time timestamp for each reading. Ideal for monitoring organic matter in environmental experiments.

