## ğŸ“¦ System Overview

- **Load Cell Group 1:** Four load cells â†’ HX711 â†’ Arduino
- **Load Cell Group 2:** One load cell â†’ HX711 â†’ Arduino
- Both groups provide separate outputs and are saved with timestamps.
- Data is written to an SD card in CSV format.

